curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/6853' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM2225", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM2225 is a high voltage, low noise and low  dropout voltage linear regulator. It is capable of  supplying 800mA output current with typical dropout  voltage of only 450mV. The operating input voltage  range is from 3.6V to 36V.  Other features include logic-controlled shutdown mode,  short-circuit current limit and thermal shutdown  protection. The SGM2225 has automatic discharge  function to quickly discharge VOUT in the disabled status.  The SGM2225 is available in Green SOT-223-3,  SOT-89-3, SOIC-8, TDFN-3×3-8L and TO-263-5B  packages. It operates over an operating temperature  range of -40℃ to +125℃.    "}'
